Quasi-geostrophic pseudo-spectral 2-d fluid simulation; a LANL-Balu production.

We will write in C, and gosh darnit, we're gonna like it!

Also, the simulation will enjoy fftw-mpi.


Also, http://www.kernel.org/doc/Documentation/CodingStyle, with the following
modifications:
    * multi-dimensional arrays may be looped over without indenting each loop:
        for(int i = 0; i < N; i++)
	for(int j = 0; j < M; j++)
	for(int k = 0; k < P; k++) {
	        do_stuff();
	}
